#: ../../source/api/actor.md:1
msgid "Actor"
msgstr "Actor"

#: ../../source/api/actor.md:3
msgid ""
"Actors can communicate through messages when this is easier to read than "
"passing object references around."
msgstr ""
"Actors koennen ueber Nachrichten kommunizieren, wenn das leichter zu "
"lesen ist als direkte Objektverweise."

#: ../../source/api/actor.md:6
msgid ""
"Combine `send_message(...)` with `@register_message(\"...\")` for simple,"
" beginner-friendly event flows between actor classes."
msgstr ""
"Kombiniere `send_message(...)` mit `@register_message(\"...\")` fuer "
"einfache, anfaengerfreundliche Event-Ablaufe zwischen Actor-Klassen."

#: ../../source/api/actor.md:9
msgid ""
"For beginner classes, you can enable `world.learning_mode = True`. In "
"this mode, common input mistakes are handled more gently where possible "
"(for example list positions are accepted in many Actor position methods)."
msgstr "Für Einsteigergruppen kannst du `world.learning_mode = True` aktivieren. In diesem Modus werden häufige Eingabefehler nach Möglichkeit toleranter behandelt, zum Beispiel werden Listenpositionen in vielen Actor-Positionsmethoden akzeptiert."

#: ../../source/api/actor.md:13
msgid "Useful beginner aliases on Actor include:"
msgstr "Nutzliche Anfaenger-Aliasse auf Actor sind:"

#: ../../source/api/actor.md:15
#, fuzzy
msgid "`go_to(...)` for `move_to(...)`"
msgstr "- `go_to(...)` fuer `move_to(...)`"

#: ../../source/api/actor.md:16
#, fuzzy
msgid "`move_forward(...)` for `move(...)`"
msgstr "- `move_forward(...)` fuer `move(...)`"

#: ../../source/api/actor.md:17
#, fuzzy
msgid "`face(...)` for `set_direction(...)`"
msgstr "- `face(...)` fuer `set_direction(...)`"

#: ../../source/api/actor.md:18
#, fuzzy
msgid "`turn(...)` for `turn_right(...)`"
msgstr "- `turn(...)` fuer `turn_right(...)`"

#: ../../source/api/actor.md:19
#, fuzzy
msgid "`touching(...)` and `touching_all(...)` for detect helpers"
msgstr "- `touching(...)` und `touching_all(...)` fuer Detect-Helfer"

#: ../../source/api/actor.md:21
msgid "API Reference"
msgstr "API-Referenz"

#: miniworlds.actors.actor.Actor:1 of
msgid "Interactive object placed in a world."
msgstr "Interaktives Objekt, das in einer Welt platziert wird."

#: miniworlds.actors.actor.Actor:3 of
msgid ""
"Actors can move, change costumes, detect collisions, send messages, and "
"react to keyboard, mouse, and lifecycle events."
msgstr "Actors können sich bewegen, Kostüme wechseln, Kollisionen erkennen, Nachrichten senden und auf Tastatur-, Maus- und Lebenszyklusereignisse reagieren."

